Name: Tylenol
Description: Tylenol Rapid Release Gels work at the speed of life to temporarily relieve minor aches and pains and reduce fever.Tylenol Rapid Release Gels can be used to help treat minor aches and pains related to headache, backache, minor arthritis pain, toothaches, pain due to the common cold, premenstrual and menstrual cramps.

Name: ibuprofen
Description: Ibuprofen is used to relieve pain from various conditions such as headache, dental pain, menstrual cramps, muscle aches, or arthritis. It is also used to reduce fever and to relieve minor aches and pain due to the common cold or flu.
